withoutTypeInference

ModelBuilder.UriValidationSettings withoutTypeInference()
Declares that the model to be created will not inference types of the rdf nodes while triples are added to the model.

Namespace dependencies will not be found without inference of nodes' types.

Method Model.retypeNodes() can still be called at any time in the model and will have the same effect, as it would have if typing inference was used. However, any triples added after the call of method Model.retypeNodes() will not update the types of the affected triples.

Returns:
an object to handle the rest of the procedure of the model creation
See Also:
Model#retypeNodes()}
